,{"id":14,"depth":103,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":103,"text":23},{"id":728,"depth":103,"text":729},"JavaScript","2020-05-18 08:20:50","Last time we learned how to draw geometric shapes in PIXI. Now it's time for something I find pretty interesting — collision detection. If you've ever Googled \"PIXI hitTestRectangle\" and hit a wall, this post explains why, and shows you a couple of ready-to-use functions you can drop straight into your project.","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002Fpixijs-v5-tutorial-15-bump","2",{"title":6,"description":759},false,"en\u002FJavaScript\u002Fpixijs-v5-tutorial-15-bump",[770,771,757,772,773],"PixiJS V5 教學","PixiJS","Canvas","w3HexSchool",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2020\u002F05\u002F18\u002Fpixijs-v5-tutorial-15-bump\u002F","eMqlIxoXqcCa2bE212gQUD7ZpIM8EwcX0N8mOEoe7-w",{"newer":778,"older":782},{"url":779,"title":780,"date":781},"\u002Fen\u002Fvue\u002F2020\u002F05\u002F22\u002Fadd-eslint-to-vue-cli\u002F","How to Add ESLint to Vue CLI","2020-05-22 23:48:14",{"url":783,"title":784,"date":785},"\u002Fen\u002Fcss\u002F2020\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcss-design-patterns-bem\u002F","CSS Design Patterns — BEM","2020-05-17 15:33:48",[787,792,797],{"url":788,"title":789,"date":790,"readingMinutes":791},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F10\u002Fweb-crypto-api-encryption-guide\u002F","No crypto Package, No Node.js — The Web Crypto API Does It All in the Browser","2026-03-10 09:45:08","9",{"url":793,"title":794,"date":795,"readingMinutes":796},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F08\u002Fjquery-why-it-declined\u002F","jQuery Was Once King — So Why Did It Fall Off?","2025-12-08 21:35:24","7",{"url":798,"title":799,"date":800,"readingMinutes":801},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F05\u002Fjavascript-generator-functions\u002F","What Are JavaScript Generator Functions (function*)? The Function You Can Pause and Resume","2025-12-05 13:40:31","5",1784011701024]